    {
      "text": "Valkyrie no Bōken: Toki no Kagi Densetsu is a role-playing action-adventure game developed and published by Namco. It was released in Japan for the Family Computer on August 1, 1986. It was also released for the Virtual Console on multiple Nintendo consoles, for the Wii on March 20, 2007, for the Nintendo 3DS on September 4, 2013, and for the Wii U on February 4, 2015.",
